No. 514,

Misc.

Potter et al. v. California. William A. Dougherty for petitioners. Thomas C. Lynch, Attorney General, William E. James, Assistant Attorney General, and James H. Kline, Deputy Attorney General, for respondent.

Sup. Ct. Cal. Motion for leave to supplement petition granted. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Douglas is of the opinion that certiorari should be granted.
